        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple operations, including an update and a conditional select with joins. The logic is straightforward but involves understanding the relationships between tables and the conditions for determining if an account is invoiced."
        }
